OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGrey and cloudy with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain through the day. Cloud
OL,7,Fbreaking up into the evening, with
OL,8,Fsome late sunny spells developing,
OL,9,Fhowever some heavy showers also
OL,10,Fpossible. Winds remain blustery
OL,11,Fthroughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers clear
OL,14,Fsoutheastward into the night, with
OL,15,Fclear spells developing in behind
OL,16,Fproviding some late sunshine across
OL,17,Fnorthern parts. Clear skies overnight
OL,18,Fwill lead to a chilly start.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
