OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy through the morning
OL,6,Fwith patchy light rain at times. Drier
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon, with some
OL,8,Fbrighter spells. Winds strengthening
OL,9,Flater, strong inland with coastal
OL,10,Fgales into the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,13,Fwinds and coastal gales easing Sunday
OL,14,Fmorning, followed by the odd blustery
OL,15,Fshower from the northwest. Sunshine
OL,16,Fand light winds Monday; breezier
OL,17,FTuesday but staying dry and sunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
